      {"type":"info","title":"Шаблон для React/Next.js проекта","markdown":"## CLAUDE.md для React/Next.js\n\n```markdown\n# Project: MyApp (Next.js 14)\n\n## Tech Stack\n- Next.js 14 (App Router)\n- TypeScript 5.5 strict\n- Tailwind CSS v4\n- Prisma ORM + PostgreSQL\n- NextAuth.js for auth\n\n## Commands\n- `npm run dev` — dev server (port 3000)\n- `npm test` — vitest\n- `npm run lint` — eslint\n- `npx prisma db push` — sync schema\n\n## Architecture\n- `app/` — Next.js App Router pages\n- `components/` — React components\n  - `ui/` — shadcn/ui base components\n  - `features/` — feature components\n- `lib/` — utilities, configs\n- `prisma/` — schema and migrations\n\n## Code Style\n- Server Components by default\n- 'use client' only when needed\n- Named exports\n- Tailwind for all styling\n\n## Rules\n- NEVER use Pages Router (app/ only)\n- NEVER use default exports\n- ALWAYS add loading.tsx for async pages\n```"},
      {"type":"highlight-text","instruction":"Выберите специфичные для Next.js правила","segments":[{"text":"Server Components by default","correct":True},{"text":"'use client' only when needed","correct":True},{"text":"app/ Router only","correct":True},{"text":"Use functional components","correct":False},{"text":"loading.tsx for async pages","correct":True},{"text":"Named exports","correct":False}]},
      {"type":"info","title":"Шаблон для Python/FastAPI проекта","markdown":"## CLAUDE.md для FastAPI\n\n```markdown\n# Project: API Service (FastAPI)\n\n## Tech Stack\n- Python 3.12, FastAPI 0.110\n- SQLAlchemy 2.0 (async)\n- Alembic for migrations\n- Pydantic v2 for schemas\n- pytest + httpx for testing\n\n## Commands\n- `uvicorn app.main:app --reload` — dev server\n- `pytest` — run tests\n- `alembic upgrade head` — apply migrations\n- `alembic revision --autogenerate -m \"desc\"` — new migration\n\n## Architecture\n- `app/main.py` — FastAPI app entry\n- `app/routers/` — API endpoints\n- `app/models/` — SQLAlchemy models\n- `app/schemas/` — Pydantic schemas\n- `app/services/` — business logic\n- `app/dependencies.py` — DI\n\n## Code Style\n- Async everywhere (async def)\n- Type hints on all functions\n- Pydantic schema for every endpoint\n- Dependency injection via Depends()\n\n## Rules\n- NEVER use raw SQL — use SQLAlchemy ORM\n- NEVER return model directly — use Pydantic schema\n- ALWAYS validate input with Pydantic\n```"},
      {"type":"code-puzzle","question":"Составьте секцию Commands для FastAPI-проекта","items":["## Commands","- `uvicorn app.main:app --reload` — dev server","- `pytest` — run tests","- `alembic upgrade head` — apply migrations","- `alembic revision --autogenerate -m \"desc\"` — new migration"]},
      {"type":"quiz","question":"Какое правило специфично для FastAPI CLAUDE.md?","options":[{"id":"a","text":"NEVER return model directly — use Pydantic schema","correct":True},{"id":"b","text":"Use functional components","correct":False},{"id":"c","text":"Server Components by default","correct":False},{"id":"d","text":"Use Tailwind for styling","correct":False}]},
      {"type":"info","title":"Шаблон для мобильного приложения","markdown":"## CLAUDE.md для React Native / Flutter\n\n### React Native:\n```markdown\n# Project: MobileApp (React Native)\n\n## Tech Stack\n- React Native 0.74, Expo SDK 51\n- TypeScript strict\n- React Navigation v6\n- Zustand for state\n\n## Commands\n- `npx expo start` — dev server\n- `npm test` — jest tests\n- `npx expo run:ios` — iOS build\n- `npx expo run:android` — Android build\n\n## Rules\n- NEVER use inline styles — use StyleSheet.create\n- ALWAYS test on both iOS and Android\n- PREFER React Navigation for all routing\n- AVOID platform-specific code when possible\n```\n\n### Принцип:\nКаждый тип проекта имеет свои специфические команды, архитектуру и ограничения. CLAUDE.md должен это отражать."},
      {"type":"matching","pairs":[{"left":"Next.js","right":"app/ Router, Server Components"},{"left":"FastAPI","right":"async def, Pydantic schemas"},{"left":"React Native","right":"StyleSheet.create, Expo"},{"left":"Все проекты","right":"Tech Stack, Commands, Rules"}]},
      {"type":"category-sort","categories":["Next.js CLAUDE.md","FastAPI CLAUDE.md","React Native CLAUDE.md"],"items":[{"text":"Server Components by default","category":"Next.js CLAUDE.md"},{"text":"NEVER use raw SQL","category":"FastAPI CLAUDE.md"},{"text":"NEVER use inline styles","category":"React Native CLAUDE.md"},{"text":"loading.tsx for async pages","category":"Next.js CLAUDE.md"},{"text":"Pydantic schema for every endpoint","category":"FastAPI CLAUDE.md"},{"text":"Test on iOS and Android","category":"React Native CLAUDE.md"}]},
      {"type":"terminal-sim","prompt":"Посмотрите содержимое текущего CLAUDE.md","expectedCommand":"cat CLAUDE.md","output":"# Project: MyApp\n\n## Tech Stack\n- React 19, TypeScript 5.5\n- Tailwind CSS v4\n\n## Commands\n- npm run dev\n- npm test\n\n## Rules\n- NEVER use default exports","hint":"Используйте cat для чтения файла"},
      {"type":"true-false","statement":"Один шаблон CLAUDE.md подходит для всех типов проектов.","correct":False},
      {"type":"code-puzzle","question":"Составьте Rules для React Native проекта","items":["## Rules","- NEVER use inline styles — use StyleSheet.create","- ALWAYS test on both iOS and Android","- PREFER React Navigation for routing","- AVOID platform-specific code"]},
      {"type":"multi-select","question":"Какие секции обязательны в любом CLAUDE.md?","options":[{"id":"a","text":"Tech Stack","correct":True},{"id":"b","text":"Commands","correct":True},{"id":"c","text":"Platform-specific notes","correct":False},{"id":"d","text":"Rules","correct":True},{"id":"e","text":"Deploy instructions","correct":False}]},
